WEBVTT

00:05.449 --> 00:07.029
Bear in mind.

00:07.806 --> 00:10.089
It means to remember something.

00:12.321 --> 00:16.538
Bear in mind that it might rain today so bring an umbrella with you.

00:19.637 --> 00:24.308
My grandfather's old so bear in mind to speak to him slowly.

00:26.685 --> 00:31.869
To pass this subject, bear in mind that you need to pass all three exams.

